 100D			      C load_required_asset_banks:
			      C     ; Post-boot banks keep bulky read-only content off the stage-two segment.
			      C     ; The generated bank layout include defines the on-disk LBA ranges, while
			      C     ; each bank still loads into one conventional-memory segment.
 100D  50		      C     push ax
 100E  53		      C     push bx
 100F  51		      C     push cx
 1010  52		      C     push dx
 1011  06		      C     push es
			      C 
